Eleventh Avenue, east side, north from and including 49th Strect. 682 Eleventh Avenue, at the S.E. corner of 49th Street, is Porn 2. Hardart's Lunch and Day-Old Bake Shop, erected in 1928. 684 Eleventh Avenue, on the N.E. corner, with the adjoining building, has just been demolished. In bhe block abovo, 708-710 Eleventh Avenue, between 50th and 5lst Streets, is to be demolished in 1935.
April 15, 1934.
P. L. Sperr.
